{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"BeforeUnloadEvent","mdn_url":"/ru/docs/Web/API/BeforeUnloadEvent","locale":"ru","native":"Русский","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ru/docs/Web/API/BeforeUnloadEvent\"><code>BeforeUnloadEvent</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Наследование:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ru/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>Событие <strong><code>beforeunload </code></strong>  (en: перед_выгрузкой) происходит (непосредственно) перед выгрузкой окна, документа и их ресурсов.</p>\n\n<p>Если присвоено ненулевое значение свойству <code>returnValue</code> Event, всплывает диалоговое окно: \"Вы действительно хотите покинуть эту страницу?\" (см. пример ниже). Если значение не присвоено, то событие не отображается. В некоторых случаях диалоговое окно всплывает только после взаимодействия пользователя с фреймом или любым встроенным фреймом. См. детали  <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">Browser compatibility</a> </p>\n\n<table class=\"properties\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Всплывающие окна</td>\n   <td>Нет</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Возможность отмены</td>\n   <td>Да</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Целевые Объекты</td>\n   <td>defaultView</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Интерфейс</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/ru/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"примеры","title":"Примеры","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:js; notranslate\"><code>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"beforeunload\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> <span class=\"token parameter\">event</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>returnValue <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\\o/\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">//is equivalent to</span>\nwindow<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"beforeunload\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> <span class=\"token parameter\">event</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">preventDefault</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Webkit-based browsers не следуют спецификации диалоговых окон . Самый кросс-браузерный работающий пример выглядит примерно так: см. ниже.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"beforeunload\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> confirmationMessage <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\\o/\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>e <span class=\"token operator\">||</span> window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>event<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>returnValue <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> confirmationMessage<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>     <span class=\"token comment\">//Gecko + IE</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> confirmationMessage<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>                                <span class=\"token comment\">//Webkit, Safari, Chrome etc.</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Совместимость браузеров","id":"совместимость_браузеров","isH3":false,"query":"api.BeforeUnloadEvent","dataURL":"/ru/docs/Web/API/BeforeUnloadEvent/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\">\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"смотрите_также","title":"Смотрите также","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/DOMContentLoaded_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">DOMContentLoaded (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/readystatechange_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">readystatechange (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/load_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">load (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/beforeunload_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">beforeunload (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/unload_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">unload (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li><a href=\"https://www.whatwg.org/specs/web-apps/current-work/#prompt-to-unload-a-document\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Выгрузка Документов - Запрос на выгрузку документа</a> </li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Примеры","id":"примеры"},{"text":"Совместимость браузеров","id":"совместимость_браузеров"},{"text":"Смотрите также","id":"смотрите_также"}],"summary":"Событие beforeunload   (en: перед_выгрузкой) происходит (непосредственно) перед выгрузкой окна, документа и их ресурсов.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"BeforeUnloadEvent","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"BeforeUnloadEvent","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"BeforeUnloadEvent","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"BeforeUnloadEvent","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ru/web/api/beforeunloadevent","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ru/web/api/beforeunloadevent/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ru/docs/Web","title":"Веб-технологии для разработчиков"},{"uri":"/ru/docs/Web/API","title":"Интерфейсы веб API"},{"uri":"/ru/docs/Web/API/BeforeUnloadEvent","title":"BeforeUnloadEvent"}],"pageTitle":"BeforeUnloadEvent - Интерфейсы веб API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}